theless, among these two molecules, we expect SO2 detection\nto be more common, as it is detectable in scenarios more favoured by formation\nmodels. We conclude that H2S and SO2 will most likely be detected in the coming\nyears with the JWST and that the detection of these species will provide\ninformation on atmospheric processes and planet formation scenarios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 31 Jul 2022 16:38:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Nov 2022 05:54:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-01"}
