anical applications. Our results shift the paradigm of compressed\npulses to the field of acoustic phonons and pave the way for a SAW-driven\nplatform of single-electron transport that is precise, synchronized, and\nscalable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 31 Jul 2022 18:27:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-16"}
