n and retrieval tasks, indicating the\npotential of rotation invariance in the field of dermoscopy images.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2022 06:15:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2022 09:06:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-03"}
