nand ringdown phases is much longer than that of the input waveform due to the\neffect of back-scattering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2022 08:11:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2022 05:52:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-29"}
